introduction: Abeddel u qettun n Commons d afecku i yettaǧan aseqdac ad iseglem s uqettun tugniwin akked ugbur agetmidya deg Wikimedia Commons, mebla ma ibeddel s ufus yal tugna. Tzemreḍ ad tissineḍ ugar deg usebter-is Wikimedia Commons.
introduction-bugs: Ma temlaled-d ibugen deg ufecku-a, azen-it-id ma ulac aɣilif, rnu tawuri deg Wikimadia Phabricator.
option-display-images: Fren amḍan n tugniwin ara d-yettwaseknen
